@$OpenBSD: patch-src_colors_c,v 1.3 2014/09/02 08:44:16 dcoppa Exp $

"Fix" screen corruption in ncmpc. Colors and attributes can not be mixed.
Colors are in the low 8 bit, mask them in the appropriate places.

